    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Inspect of lid, cornea, sclera\nSlit lamp exam\nIntraocular pressure\nAfter exclusion of\nGlobe Rupture\nBloodwork (CBC, BMP, ESR, CRP) only if considering endogenous endophthalmitis\nOcular ultrasound\nto look for alternative diagnosis\nAfter exclusion of\nGlobe Rupture",
