    "Management": {
      "text": "Emergent ophtho consult (for gram stain/culture and definitive treatment of intravitreal\nantibiotics\n)\nSystemic\nantibiotics\nfor endogenous endophthalmitis (rare cause)\nSystemic antibiotics for other etiologies is controversial\nAntibiotic prophylaxis in\nGlobe Rupture\nreduces incidence of endophthalmitis to <1%\ntetanus, if indicated",
